    "feat": {
        "name": "Doctor's Visitation",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You move to provide immediate care to those who need it. You Stride, then use Battle Medicine or Treat Poison. You can spend 2 actions for Doctor\u2019s Visitation to instead Stride and then use either Administer First Aid or Treat Condition (if you have that feat).",
